<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王后退了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去有点儿疑惑：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那药丸顺着我的喉咙跳下去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个洞穴里亮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精用力闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他再睁开眼睛的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨站在了他的面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨！”黑熊精大叫道，“你骗了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上把袈裟还回来。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！黑熊精说。“我不想......啊......啊......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捂着肚子不停地呻吟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”悟空的声音响了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精四处看了看，很惊讶：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到了那猴子的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跪了下来，又开始呻吟：“你在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在你身体里！”悟空说，“我变成了药丸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我要练练我的打斗能力！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在黑熊精身体里又踢又打。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘣！砰！嘣！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”黑风王大叫，在地上滚来滚去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空上蹿下跳，不停翻滚，跑来跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请停下！”黑风王大叫，“你弄疼我的肚子了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把袈裟还回来！”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会的，我保证！”黑熊精说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都听你的！请让那猴子停下吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨拿出了一个金属头箍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那看上去就和悟空头上戴的一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把那头箍戴在了黑熊精的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，现在出来吧。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小小的悟空从黑风王的鼻子里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他迅速恢复到了原样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“袈裟在哪里？”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精指向了洞穴深处一个黑乎乎的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空去拿袈裟时，黑风王朝着观音菩萨猛冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精的速度太慢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨向他又扔了四个金属箍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个夹住了他的手腕，另外两个夹住了他的脚踝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨开始念咒，黑熊精尖叫：“请停下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你保证向善吗？”观音菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是！”黑风王回答，“我保证。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿着袈裟回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见黑熊，就笑了：“你戴了五个箍！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王看着地面叹气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿到袈裟了，观音菩萨。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该怎么处置这只熊精？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会对他宽容一些。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他表现好，可以在普陀山上做我的护卫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨领着黑熊出了洞穴，消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞回了寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你拿到袈裟了！”唐僧看到悟空时，叫了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿回来了。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这两个人继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空把他和黑熊精的经历都告诉了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我杀了那个道士。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他实际上是只邪恶的狼精。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨把自己扮成了那只狼精。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你就变成了药丸。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我直接进了那只熊的肚子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑，“他很惊讶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧微笑：“我觉得我们都得到了很好的教训，悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不会再向任何人展示这件袈裟了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“袈裟是佛祖给的礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须小心......”悟空不再说话，抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“附近有个妖怪。”他看向附近的一个洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里有人哼哼。唐僧害怕地浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个长得像猪一样的怪物从洞穴里跳了出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手里拿着一个重重的钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>